Inverse hyperbolic sine, element-wise.

@description

# Examples
```{r}
x <- k_convert_to_tensor(c(1, -1, 0))
k_arcsinh(x)
```

@returns
Output tensor of same shape as `x`.

@param x
Input tensor.
